{"tid":1535912,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"全世界人注意！！！9月7日入機場全世界遊客look!","createTime":"2019-09-03T13:52:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T09:31:58.000Z","uid":273740,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5be4c012d1f2481efc3d0fe531f66fcf169f8885","tid":1535912,"uid":273740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T13:52:17.000Z","msg":"入機場唔同係地區打陣地戰，d 狗就算知你係示威者都唔會開槍，更何況如果佢唔肯定你係遊客定示威者？我地以往著黑衫帶口罩既原因係因為要分辨自己人，但入機場係唔洗，無論你係咩立場，只要你出現係機場，夠人多，就做到我地既目標！<br />\n<br />\n參考過上次既情況，好多真。遊客係會老遠行入機場，到時就算我地行馬路，佢地都唔會知我地去機場既目的！！<br />\n<br />\n再者，對上次d 狗喺東涌捉到人，都係因為黑衫口罩！ 今次如果個撚個都遊客look, 一離開左機場範圍，佢地就算鳩捉人，都唔會好似以前咁放肆！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>所以9月7號！ 全世界遊客look 參觀機場！</strong></span>"},{"pid":"9b02e644fa484b5ff9d5f74a219c27273a536142","tid":1535912,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T13:53:12.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n